results.name: Wmns UltraBoost 21 'White Hazy Rose'
results.story: The adidas women’s UltraBoost 21 ‘White Hazy Rose’ highlights subtle pops of color on a performance runner designed for enhanced energy return. A stark white finish distinguishes a Primeknit upper that incorporates Primeblue, a high-performance material made in part with Parley Ocean Plastic. A translucent heel counter in a contrasting dark pink hue provides rearfoot support. The sneaker is mounted on a full-length Boost midsole, designed to yield a more responsive ride with the addition of a revised Torsion system dubbed Linear Energy Push.

results.name: UltraBoost 21 'Grey Screaming Orange'
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost 21 ‘Grey Screaming Orange’ features sharply contrasting hues on the sock-like Primeknit upper. The two-tone knit construction is reinforced with a semi-translucent midfoot cage and a molded heel counter in a gradient purple and orange finish. The lightweight build is mounted on a full-length Boost midsole, shaped with an exaggerated heel curve and enhanced with Linear Energy Push, a revised Torsion system designed to yield a more responsive ride.

Wmns UltraBoost 21 'Hazy Rose'
results.story: The adidas women’s UltraBoost 21 ‘Hazy Rose’ showcases a monochromatic finish throughout the exterior of the running shoe. The lightweight Primeknit upper, featuring recycled Parley Ocean Plastic and zero virgin polyester, sits atop a full-length Boost midsole with 6% more Boost capsules than previous UltraBoost models. A revised Torsion system, dubbed Linear Energy Push, provides less flex in the forefoot for a more responsive ride.

results.name: UltraBoost 21 'Grey Screaming Orange'
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost 21 'Grey Screaming Orange' marries responsive cushioning with a sustainable build. The sock-like upper is constructed from breathable grey Primeknit, partially made with recycled materials that include Parley Ocean Plastic. The neutral palette is disrupted by a gradient blend of orange and purple on the translucent heel counter. A redesigned Torsion system enhances the Boost midsole, reinforced underfoot with Continental rubber in high-wear areas.

results.name: adidas Ultra Boost DNA CC1 Cloud White
results.story: The adidas UltraBoost DNA CC_1 ‘Cloud White’ draws inspiration from brand’s popular Climacool models from the early 2000s. The pristine white Primeknit upper, partially made with recycled materials that include Parley Ocean Plastic, features a midfoot RPU cage with cooling aerodynamic air channels. Classic Climacool branding adorns the leather tongue patch. The ventilated build rides on a full-length Boost midsole, supported by a Stretchweb Continental rubber outsole.

Wmns Terrex Agravic TR 'Hazy Emerald'
results.story: The adidas women’s Terrex Agravic TR 'Hazy Emerald' highlights pastel tones on a rugged low-top built for outdoor adventures. Breathable mesh construction on the upper is fortified with synthetic abrasion-resistant overlays in bright teal finish. An integrated lacing system delivers midfoot lockdown, while an external heel counter in Hazy Orange provides rearfoot stability. The same hue is repeated on a lightweight EVA midsole, supported by a lugged Continental rubber outsole.

results.name: ZX 2K Infant 'Wordmark Heel Stripe - White'
results.story: The adidas ZX 2K Infant ‘Wordmark Heel Stripe’ provides a modern take on the brand’s ZX running heritage for little feet. A crisp white finish is executed on the lightweight textile upper, accented with a seamless overlay that wraps around the heel and features a repeating adidas wordmark in white-on-navy block lettering. Plush cushioning comes courtesy of an exaggerated foam midsole, partially caged for rearfoot support and durability.

results.name: Takahashi Hiroko x Wmns Adilette Shower Slide 'Black White'
results.story: Designed in partnership with the Japanese textile artist, the Takahashi Hiroko x adidas women’s Adilette Shower Slide ‘Black White’ updates the versatile slip-on with a glossy patent-leather bandage strap, decorated with the brand’s signature three-stripes and lined in soft textile for a comfortable fit. The lightweight and durable EVA midsole is layered up top with a plush Cloudfoam footbed. Underfoot, a herringbone-traction outsole delivers grippy traction.

results.name: X Ghosted+ FG 'Solar Yellow'
results.story: A firm-ground soccer cleat built for speed, the adidas X Ghosted+ FG ‘Solar Yellow’ features a vibrant finish that amplifies an airy, laceless upper constructed from composite Mirageskin. A low-cut Clawcollar provides a locked-in fit and full range of motion, while the raised forefoot allows for a clean strike zone. Underfoot, the outsole is enhanced with a Carbitex carbon-fiber insert for a springy sense of propulsion, along with chevron-shaped studs for grippy traction.
